<section id="about" class="about">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="content">
			<h2 class="fade-in">About</h2>
			<div class="about-content">
				<div class="bio fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
					<p>
						I'm a senior UI/UX and product designer with a passion for creating meaningful digital experiences.
						My work focuses on understanding user needs, solving complex problems, and delivering elegant solutions.
					</p>
					<p>
						With expertise in design systems, user research, and product strategy, I bridge the gap between
						user needs and business goals. I believe great design is invisible—it just works.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonials fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
					<article class="testimonial">
						<p class="testimonial-quote">"Christina is one of the sharpest minds I've worked with. Her ability to navigate complex challenges, think systemically, and collaborate with empathy made her an invaluable partner as a designer. She consistently brings clarity and intelligence to difficult problems."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">— Christopher Nemeth, Lead Product Designer, OOUX specialist</p>
					</article>

					<article class="testimonial">
						<p class="testimonial-quote">"Christina has a rare ability to turn complex, fast-moving ideas into clear, thoughtful, and genuinely effective designs. She brings calm, clarity, and empathy to collaboration, and consistently makes teams better through how she listens and works with others."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">— Abdul Wahab, Technical Project Manager</p>
					</article>

					<article class="testimonial">
						<p class="testimonial-quote">"Christina balances clarity, usability, and technical reality with ease. She collaborates closely with engineering, adapts designs to real constraints, and translates complex requirements into intuitive, implementation-ready solutions."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">— Eugene Yakhnenko, Senior Frontend Software Engineer</p>
					</article>
				</div>

				<div class="skills fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
					<h3>Skills & Expertise</h3>
					<div class="skills-grid">
						<div class="skill-category">
							<h4>Design</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>UI/UX Design</li>
								<li>Design Systems</li>
								<li>Prototyping</li>
								<li>Visual Design</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-category">
							<h4>Research</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>User Research</li>
								<li>Usability Testing</li>
								<li>User Interviews</li>
								<li>Analytics</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-category">
							<h4>Tools</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>Figma</li>
								<li>Adobe Creative Suite</li>
								<li>Sketch</li>
								<li>Principle</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.about h2 {
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
	}

	.about-content {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--spacing-lg);
	}

	.bio p {
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.bio p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.testimonials {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.testimonial {
		max-width: 640px;
	}

	.testimonial-quote {
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.skills h3 {
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.skills-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.skill-category h4 {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.skill-category ul {
		list-style: none;
	}

	.skill-category li {
		padding: 0.25rem 0;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.skills-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
